=head1 DESCRIPTION

This entity describes a job template. Job template stores values of
StartJobRun API request in a template and can be used to start a job
run. Job template allows two use cases: avoid repeating recurring
StartJobRun API request values, enforcing certain values in StartJobRun
API request.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 Arn => Str

The ARN of the job template.


=head2 CreatedAt => Str

The date and time when the job template was created.


=head2 CreatedBy => Str

The user who created the job template.


=head2 DecryptionError => Str

The error message in case the decryption of job template fails.


=head2 Id => Str

The ID of the job template.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> JobTemplateData => L<Paws::EMRContainers::JobTemplateData>

The job template data which holds values of StartJobRun API request.


=head2 KmsKeyArn => Str

The KMS key ARN used to encrypt the job template.


=head2 Name => Str

The name of the job template.


=head2 Tags => L<Paws::EMRContainers::TagMap>

The tags assigned to the job template.



